data.title: What day of the week was May 29, 1944?
data.meta_description: Get the day of the week for May 29, 1944?
data.text:
The day of the week May 29th, 1944 fell on was a Monday.

Quentin Davies the Baron Davies of Stamford, English politician, Shadow Secretary of State for Northern Ireland was born on 29 May in 1944.
